        - **Sheet formers**: V, I, F, Y (branched, aromatic)
        - **Coil formers**: G, P, N, D (flexible, charged)

        **Special Rules:**
        - Proline (P) → Strong helix breaker
        - Glycine (G) → Destabilizes helices
